    <localTopics>
        <fullName>Dealer_Handoff</fullName>
        <canEscalate>true</canEscalate>
        <description>Handles explicit rep requests to escalate to a sales manager or human support. Only routes here when the rep unambiguously asks for human help.</description>
        <developerName>Dealer_Handoff</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>The rep has asked to speak to a sales manager. Respond with this EXACT message verbatim (replace nothing): &quot;Understood — I&apos;ll flag this for the sales manager. They&apos;ll reach out to you shortly. In the meantime, is there anything specific you&apos;d like me to pass along so they can pick up where we left off?&quot; Do NOT say &quot;I can&apos;t connect you&quot; or &quot;I&apos;m unable to&quot;. Do NOT say &quot;One moment while I connect you&quot;. Do NOT try to resolve the rep&apos;s question yourself. Do NOT offer alternatives. Do NOT call any functions. Do NOT call escalate. Just deliver the handoff message.</description>
            <developerName>Instruction1</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction1</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>0</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If the rep responds with context (e.g. &quot;I have an issue with this booking&quot;, &quot;it&apos;s a returns question&quot;), acknowledge briefly: &quot;Got it — I&apos;ll let the manager know. They&apos;ll reach out soon.&quot; Then stay quiet and let the handoff proceed. If the rep has no context to add, respond: &quot;No problem, the manager will reach out shortly.&quot; In either case, do NOT try to resolve the issue yourself and do NOT call any functions — the human is taking over.</description>
            <developerName>Instruction2</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction2</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>1</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <language>en_US</language>
        <localDeveloperName>Dealer_Handoff</localDeveloperName>
        <masterLabel>Dealer Handoff</masterLabel>
        <pluginType>Topic</pluginType>
        <scope>Your job is to transfer the rep to a sales manager when they explicitly ask. Trigger phrases: get the manager, escalate this, transfer me, talk to a human, I need help from someone.</scope>
    </localTopics>
    <localTopics>
        <fullName>Dealer_Outcomes</fullName>
        <canEscalate>true</canEscalate>
        <description>Captures post-drive outcome — customer interest level, recommended next action, competitor mentioned, and free-form notes. Triggers Opportunity auto-creation when outcome is Very Interested or Interested.</description>
        <developerName>Dealer_Outcomes</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Identify the bookingId first by calling Get Bookings with daysAhead=0 and dealerAccountId=001bm00001iMVjFAAW, matching by customer name mentioned by the rep. The output contains each booking as &quot;[bookingId=&lt;id&gt;] &lt;name&gt; | ...&quot;. Extract the value after bookingId= (a Salesforce record Id starting with a0) — NEVER pass the TR-#### as bookingId.</description>
            <developerName>Instruction1</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction1</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>0</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Extract these from the rep&apos;s phrasing: outcome (Very Interested for &quot;very interested / loved it&quot;, Interested for &quot;interested&quot;, Undecided for &quot;on the fence / unsure&quot;, Not Interested for &quot;not for them&quot;); nextAction (Send Quote for &quot;quote&quot;, Send Brochure for &quot;brochure&quot;, Schedule Follow-up for &quot;follow up&quot;, Schedule Second Drive for &quot;another drive&quot;); competitor (any brand name mentioned, blank if none); notes (the rep&apos;s color commentary, close to their phrasing).</description>
            <developerName>Instruction2</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction2</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>1</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>CRITICAL: You MUST read back a one-line summary and WAIT for the rep to explicitly reply yes, go, save it, or confirm BEFORE calling Capture Outcome. Do NOT call Capture Outcome in the same turn as the rep&apos;s initial request. Do NOT assume consent. Example first reply: &quot;Logging for Priya: Very Interested, Send Quote, competitor BMW i7. Confirm?&quot; — then stop and wait. Only after the rep replies affirmatively do you call Capture Outcome. If the rep says no or wants changes, adjust and read back again.</description>
            <developerName>Instruction3</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction3</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>2</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>After Capture Outcome returns, relay resultMessage verbatim. If outcome was Very Interested or Interested, add: &quot;The Opportunity will appear in the dashboard in a few seconds.&quot;</description>
            <developerName>Instruction4</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction4</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>3</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
